<HEADLINE> Eze Wins Belmont Feature </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Eze came from last in the field of six to  
register a half-length victory in the seventh running of the 
Pebbles Handicap Belmont Monday. 
</P>
<P>
	Colstar was second, a nose ahead of Jazz.  
</P>
<P>
	Eze made her move midway on the far turn. Racing wide, she  
circled her rivals and wore down the leaders in the final strides. 
</P>
<P>
