<HEADLINE> Jets-Jaguars Delayed by Turf Tear </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	EAST RUTHERFORD, N.J. (AP) -- The game between the Jacksonville  
Jaguars and New York Jets was delayed for about eight minutes 
Monday night because of a tear in the artificial turf, which is 
scheduled to be replaced next year by grass. 
</P>
